gment, then `(Γ ⇒ # s)` in the full product-free calculus iff the corresponding translated context derives `# s` in the left-only calculus; likewise for the right-only fragment.', 'statement_prelude_code': "abbrev PFTp := Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp\nabbrev LeftTp := Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Left.Tp\nabbrev RightTp := Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Right.Tp\n\ndef IsLeftOnlyTp : PFTp → Prop\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.atom _ => True\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.ldiv A B => IsLeftOnlyTp A ∧ IsLeftOnlyTp B\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.rdiv _ _ => False\n\ndef IsRightOnlyTp : PFTp → Prop\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.atom _ => True\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.ldiv _ _ => False\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.rdiv B A => IsRightOnlyTp B ∧ IsRightOnlyTp A\n\ndef IsLeftOnlyCtx (Γ : List PFTp) : Prop :=\n  ∀ A ∈ Γ, IsLeftOnlyTp A\n\ndef IsRightOnlyCtx (Γ : List PFTp) : Prop :=\n  ∀ A ∈ Γ, IsRightOnlyTp A\n\ndef leftTp? : PFTp → Option LeftTp\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.atom s =>\n      some (Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Left.Tp.atom s)\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.ldiv A B => do\n      let A' <- leftTp? A\n      let B' <- leftTp? B\n      some (Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Left.Tp.ldiv A' B')\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.rdiv _ _ => none\n\ndef rightTp? : PFTp → Option RightTp\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.atom s =>\n      some (Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Right.Tp.atom s)\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.ldiv _ _ => none\n  | Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Tp.rdiv B A => do\n      let B' <- rightTp? B\n      let A' <- rightTp? A\n      some (Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Right.Tp.rdiv B' A')\n\ndef leftCtx? (Γ : List PFTp) : Option (List LeftTp) :=\n  Γ.mapM leftTp?\n\ndef rightCtx? (Γ : List PFTp) : Option (List RightTp) :=\n  Γ.mapM rightTp?", 'formalized_stmt': '(∀ {Γ : List PFTp} {s : String},\n  IsLeftOnlyCtx Γ →\n    ((Γ ⇒ # s) ↔\n      match leftCtx? Γ with\n      | some ΓL => Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Left.Sequent ΓL (Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Left.Tp.atom s)\n      | none => False)) ∧\n(∀ {Γ : List PFTp} {s : String},\n  IsRightOnlyCtx Γ →\n    ((Γ ⇒ # s) ↔\n      match rightCtx? Γ with\n      | some ΓR => Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Right.Sequent ΓR (Mathling.Lambek.ProductFree.Right.Tp.atom s)\n      | none => False))', 'prelude_code': '', 'prover_statement_result': 'ok', 'prover_attempts_used': 2, 'priority_refresh_ran': True, 'priority_refresh_error': '', 'expand_candidates': [], 'stored_expand_rows': [], 'promoted_expand_rows': [], 'batch_generator_added_problem_rows': [], 'batch_generator_error': '', 'pending_expand_candidate_count': 9, 'archived_problem_count': 20, 'active_open_problem_count': 9, 'iteration': 19}
